arrow, shiny medium-green leaves. Abundant golden-yellow flowers.", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "Excellent year-round production in Tropical monsoon tropical climate. Continuous harvest possible.", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "GardenGuru.in (tropical monsoon climates delivery), Ugaoo (all-India delivery including tropical monsoon climates), GreenMyLife (ships to tropical monsoon climates), PlantsBazar.com (India-wide), local tropical monsoon climates nurseries. Available as seeds or plants."}, {"name": "Yerba Anís / Pericón", "slug": "yerba-an-s-peric-n", "lineage_type": "open_pollinated", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "sort_order": 1, "origin": "Traditional Mexican and Central American herb, same species as Mexican Tarragon", "traits": "Traditional strain used medicinally and in cooking. Identical botanical characteristics to Mexican Tarragon.", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "Productive year-round in tropical conditions.", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "GreenMyLife (tropical monsoon climates delivery), specialty herb suppliers in India."}, {"name": "Sweet Mace / Mexican Marigold", "slug": "sweet-mace-mexican-marigold", "lineage_type": "open_pollinated", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "sort_order": 2, "origin": "Mexico and Central America", "traits": "Same plant as Mexican Tarragon with emphasis on ornamental yellow flowers.", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "High leaf and flower production.", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "Indian seed suppliers, online nurseries delivering to tropical monsoon climates."}, {"name": "French Tarragon 🏆 ❌", "slug": "french-tarragon", "lineage_type": "heirloom", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "sort_order": 3, "origin": "Southern Europe, Central Asia (temperate regions)", "traits": "Temperate climate herb requiring cool winters and dry summers.", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "", "growing_notes": "", "availability": ""}, {"name": "Russian Tarragon 🌱 ❌", "slug": "russian-tarragon", "l